<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>DIAGNOSIS:</div><div>BENIGN</div><div>Consistent with with lymphocytic (Hashimoto) thyroiditis.</div><div><br/></div><div>TYPE OF SPECIMEN: Thyroid, ___ lobe, fine needle aspiration</div><div>ADEQUACY: Satisfactory for interpretation</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
