  <note>
    <title>T-B-Hashimoto (Not known if the patient has it)</title>
    <created>20250428T062423Z</created>
    <updated>20250428T064329Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>DIAGNOSIS:</div><div>BENIGN</div><div>Numerous polymorphic lymphoid cells and scattered oncocytic cells.</div><div>Note: The findings are suggestive of chronic lymphocytic (Hashimoto) thyroiditis in the proper clinical setting. </div><div><br/></div><div>TYPE OF SPECIMEN: Thyroid, ___ lobe, fine needle aspiration</div><div>ADEQUACY: Satisfactory for interpretation</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>T-B-Lymphocytic thyroiditis (Clinical history not provided)</title>
